TITLE: SUM Aggregation Function in SQL
DESCRIPTION: Returns the sum of input values in a numeric field. Ignores null values unless all values are null, in which case it returns null. Returns bigint for integer input and double for floating points.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/main/docs/reference/query-languages/sql/sql-functions-aggs.md#2025-04-21_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT SUM(salary) AS sum FROM emp;
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT ROUND(SUM(salary / 12.0), 1) AS sum FROM emp;
```

