TITLE: PERCENTILE Aggregation Function in SQL
DESCRIPTION: Calculates the nth percentile of input values. Supports different algorithms (tdigest or hdr) and configuration parameters for percentile calculation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/main/docs/reference/query-languages/sql/sql-functions-aggs.md#2025-04-21_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT languages, PERCENTILE(salary, 95) AS "95th" FROM emp
       GROUP BY languages;
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT languages, PERCENTILE(salary / 12.0, 95) AS "95th" FROM emp
       GROUP BY languages;
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
SELECT
    languages,
    PERCENTILE(salary, 97.3, 'tdigest', 100.0) AS "97.3_TDigest",
    PERCENTILE(salary, 97.3, 'hdr', 3) AS "97.3_HDR"
FROM emp
GROUP BY languages;
```

