LANGUAGE: esql
CODE:
```
FROM ul_logs, apps METADATA _index, _version
| WHERE id IN (13, 14) AND _version == 1
| EVAL key = CONCAT(_index, "_", TO_STR(id))
| SORT id, _index
| KEEP id, _index, _version, key
