SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/main/docs/reference/query-languages/query-dsl/query-dsl-pinned-query.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: console
CODE:
```
GET /_search
{
  "query": {
    "pinned": {
      "docs": [
        {
          "_index": "my-index-000001", <1>
          "_id": "1"
        },
        {
          "_id": "4" <2>
        }
      ],
      "organic": {
        "match": {
          "description": "iphone"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

