LANGUAGE: console
CODE:
```
POST /sales/_search?size=0
{
  "query": {
    "constant_score": {
      "filter": {
        "match": { "type": "hat" }
      }
    }
  },
  "aggs": {
    "hat_prices": {
      "sum": {
        "field": "price",
        "missing": 100
      }
    }
  }
}
```

