# Example documents
PUT my-index-000001/_doc/1
{
  "my_field": "This is a document"
}

PUT my-index-000001/_doc/2
{
  "my_field": "This is another document"
}

GET my-index-000001/_search
{
  "aggs": {
    "my_field_cardinality": {
      "cardinality": {
        "field": "my_field.hash"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

