TITLE: ESQL Parameter Documentation for Slice Function
DESCRIPTION: Defines three main parameters: field (multivalue expression), start (starting position with support for negative indices), and end (optional ending position, inclusive). Parameters support null values and negative indexing where -1 represents the last element.
