TITLE: Defining ElasticsearchException Class in Java
DESCRIPTION: Defines the ElasticsearchException class, which extends RuntimeException and implements ToXContentFragment. It includes constructors for various error scenarios and methods for handling error details.
SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/main/modules/repository-azure/licenses/reactive-streams-NOTICE.txt#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: Java
CODE:
```
public class ElasticsearchException extends RuntimeException implements ToXContentFragment {

    private final Supplier<ElasticsearchException> suppressed = new Supplier<ElasticsearchException>() {
        @Override
        public ElasticsearchException get() {
            return ElasticsearchException.this;
        }
    };

    public ElasticsearchException(StreamInput in) throws IOException {
        super(in.readOptionalString());
        readStackTrace(this, in);
        headers.addAll(in.readMapOfLists(StreamInput::readString, StreamInput::readString));
