SOURCE: https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/blob/main/docs/reference/query-languages/query-dsl/query-dsl-span-not-query.md#2025-04-21_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
GET /_search
{
  "query": {
    "span_not": {
      "include": {
        "span_term": { "field1": "hoya" }
      },
      "exclude": {
        "span_near": {
          "clauses": [
            { "span_term": { "field1": "la" } },
            { "span_term": { "field1": "hoya" } }
          ],
          "slop": 0,
          "in_order": true
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

